Package de.tum.in.tumcampus.services

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BackgroundService
    Service used to sync data in background
    DownloadService
    Service used to download files from external pages
    FillCacheService
    Service used to fill caches in background, for faster/offline access
    GcmBroadcastReceiver
    This WakefulBroadcastReceiver takes care of creating and managing a partial wake lock for your app.
    GcmIntentService
    This IntentService does the actual handling of the GCM message.
    ScanResultsAvailableReceiver
    Listens for android's ScanResultsAvailable broadcast and checks if eduroam is nearby.
    ScanResultsAvailableReceiver.NeverShowAgain  
    SilenceService
    Service used to silence the mobile during lectures
    StartSyncReceiver
    Receives on boot completed broadcast, sets alarm for next sync-try and start BackgroundService if enabled in settings
